description: As government formation talks continue, there are indications the Covid-19 recovery plan may accelerate.
title: Coronavirus: Would a new Irish government lift lockdown faster?

maintext: "It has been acknowledged it is not required by the science; it has been helpful but it cannot be allowed to block Ireland restarting activity which is already underway elsewhere without a negative impact," he said.
